      "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
      "hillId": "desert",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "想象一片沙漠。很静，很空，什么都不缺。",
      "file": "audio/voice/desert/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.11
    },
    {
      "hillId": "desert",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "念头来了，像一粒沙落在沙上。看见它，然后让它落下。",
      "file": "audio/voice/desert/5m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.69
    },
    {
      "hillId": "desert",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 210,
      "text": "呼气时，放下一样东西。再呼气，再放下一样。",
      "file": "audio/voice/desert/5m05.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
      "hillId": "desert",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 6,
      "t": 270,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……呼气……",
      "file": "audio/voice/desert/5m06.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
      "hillId": "desert",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 292,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/desert/5m07.mp3",
