      "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
      "hillId": "sakura",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "想象你坐在樱花树下。花瓣一片一片，慢慢飘落。",
      "file": "audio/voice/sakura/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.3
    },
    {
      "hillId": "sakura",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "每一口呼吸，也像一片花瓣。来了，又走了，不会再来。",
      "file": "audio/voice/sakura/5m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.17
    },
    {
      "hillId": "sakura",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 210,
      "text": "在心里轻轻说一声谢谢。给这一刻，给正在呼吸的自己。",
