    {
      "hillId": "mistvalley",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "想象你坐在山谷里，四周都是雾。看不见远处，也没关系。",
      "file": "audio/voice/mistvalley/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.76
    },
    {
      "hillId": "mistvalley",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "不确定的感觉来了，就让它来。像雾一样，停在身边。",
