      "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
      "hillId": "mistvalley",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 11,
      "t": 592,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/mistvalley/10m11.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m00.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 1,
      "t": 20,
      "text": "感受身体和座位接触的地方，让重量慢慢沉下去。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m01.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 2,
      "t": 45,
      "text": "注意你的呼吸。像风一样，它自己来，自己走。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m02.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.61
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "想象你坐在一片草原上。风来了，草浪一层一层，推向远山。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.65
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "念头来了，像风一样穿过你。不抓，也不挡。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.58
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 210,
      "text": "声音、感觉、念头，都放进这片开阔里。草原很大，装得下一切。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m05.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 7.27
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 6,
      "t": 265,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……呼气……",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m06.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 292,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/5m07.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m00.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.89
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 1,
      "t": 25,
      "text": "感受身体和座位接触的地方，让重量慢慢沉下去。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m01.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 2,
      "t": 60,
      "text": "从头到脚，慢慢放松。额头、肩膀、手心，都松下来。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m02.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.36
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 100,
      "text": "注意你的呼吸。像风一样，它自己来，自己走。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.75
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 160,
      "text": "想象你坐在一片草原上。风来了，草浪一层一层，推向远山。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.67
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 230,
      "text": "风吹过耳朵，吹过肩膀，吹过指尖。你不抓，也不挡。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m05.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 7.2
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 6,
      "t": 300,
      "text": "念头来了，像风一样穿过你。发现走神，就回到这口呼吸。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m06.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.95
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 370,
      "text": "听一听周围的声音。远的，近的，都放进这片开阔里。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m07.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 8,
      "t": 440,
      "text": "草原很大，装得下风声，也装得下你的所有念头。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m08.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.73
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 9,
      "t": 510,
      "text": "此刻你什么都不用做，只是坐着，像草原一样开阔。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m09.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.3
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 10,
      "t": 560,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……呼气……",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m10.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.18
    },
    {
      "hillId": "grassland",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 11,
      "t": 592,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/grassland/10m11.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m00.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 1,
      "t": 20,
      "text": "想象你坐在温泉边，热气一团一团，慢慢围过来。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m01.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.87
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 2,
      "t": 45,
      "text": "跟着呼吸，慢一点。吸气……一、二、三、四、五……呼气……一、二、三、四、五……",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m02.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 12.29
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "把注意力放在头顶。让一股暖意，从头顶开始，慢慢往下淌。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.31
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "暖意流过额头、眼睛、脸颊。流到肩膀时，让它沉下来，像泡进热水里。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 7.66
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 210,
      "text": "暖意继续往下，流过胸口、手心、双腿，一直到脚尖。身体每一寸，都暖暖的。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m05.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 9.07
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 6,
      "t": 265,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……慢一点……呼气……再慢一点……",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m06.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 292,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/5m07.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
