    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 370,
      "text": "暖意流过胸口和后背。心里的紧，也一点一点烫开了。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/10m07.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.47
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 8,
      "t": 440,
      "text": "暖意流到手心、双腿，一直到脚尖。连脚趾头，都暖暖的。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/10m08.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.95
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 9,
      "t": 510,
      "text": "此刻，整个身体都泡在暖意里。它记得一切，也可以放下一切。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/10m09.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.64
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 10,
      "t": 560,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……慢一点……呼气……再慢一点……",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/10m10.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
      "hillId": "hotspring",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 11,
      "t": 592,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/hotspring/10m11.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m00.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 1,
      "t": 20,
      "text": "听，远处的钟声，一下，又一下。让心跟着静下来。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m01.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.24
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 2,
      "t": 45,
      "text": "注意你的呼吸。一吸一呼，像寺前的灯，明明灭灭，却一直亮着。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m02.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 7.1
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 3,
      "t": 90,
      "text": "把心安在自己身上。默默地对自己说：愿我平安，愿我安好。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m03.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 6.24
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 4,
      "t": 150,
      "text": "想起一位你惦念的人。把这盏灯递过去：愿你平安，愿你安好。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m04.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.95
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 5,
      "t": 210,
      "text": "再把灯举得远一些。给更多的人，给所有像你我一样走着的人。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m05.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 5.93
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 6,
      "t": 265,
      "text": "最后一次深呼吸。吸气……呼气……",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m06.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 4.18
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 5,
      "index": 7,
      "t": 292,
      "text": "准备好了，就慢慢睁开眼睛。",
      "file": "audio/voice/temple/5m07.mp3",
      "ok": true,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "hillId": "temple",
      "minutes": 10,
      "index": 0,
      "t": 0,
      "text": "找一个舒服的姿势坐好，轻轻闭上眼睛。",
